-wordpress-travel-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"460\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224223\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/prevalent-wordpress-travel-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/prevalent-wordpress-travel-theme-300x178.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/prevalent-wordpress-travel-theme-768x456.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Prevalent is a professional WordPress travel theme with plenty of features and functionalities to create a travel website. Designed with travel and tourism entrepreneurs in mind, it has a clean and elegant design. </p>\n<p>The Prevalent theme allows you to showcase your best travel destinations, special offers, latest news, client testimonials, photo galleries, and everything else youâ€™ll need on a travel website. You can customize each of these sections effortlessly from the theme customizer. </p>\n<p>This theme is fully responsive and retina-ready. Therefore, your travel website will look great on all types of devices and screens. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/prevalent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Prevalent today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/mesmerize/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">26. Mesmerize</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/mesmerize/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/mesmerize-wordpress-theme-travel-demo.jpg\" alt=\"mesmerize-wordpress-theme-travel-demo\" width=\"775\" height=\"460\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224224\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/mesmerize-wordpress-theme-travel-demo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/mesmerize-wordpress-theme-travel-demo-300x178.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/mesmerize-wordpress-theme-travel-demo-768x456.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Mesmerize is a highly flexible multipurpose theme that you can use for any type of website including a travel agency site, blog, restaurant, mobile app, or eCommerce site. It comes with a powerful live editor that allows you to edit text, images, colors, add elements, and customize your page layout completely with real-time live previews. </p>\n<p>As its name implies, Mesmerize offers a truly mesmerizing website-making experience. Thereâ€™re multiple ready-to-use theme demos and 100+ predesigned blocks you can use to build beautiful pages in no time. </p>\n<p>With Mesmerize, you can use Font Awesome icons, Google Fonts, Google Maps, photo galleries, and much more. Itâ€™s a great theme that&#8217;s well worth trying out for your new travel website. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/mesmerize/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Mesmerize today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/kale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">27. Kale</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/kale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/kale-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"kale-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"521\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221828\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/kale-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/kale-wordpress-theme-300x202.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/kale-wordpress-theme-768x516.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Kale is a simple and elegant WordPress blog theme that can be used for creating travel, food, fashion, and personal blogs. It features a simple and clutter-free design that looks pleasant to the usersâ€™ eyes. Itâ€™s an SEO optimized theme so your blog content will get better ranking in search results. </p>\n<p>You can use a text or image logo in your blog, select a background color or add a background image, add multiple sidebars, social media menus, and more. It allows you to add front page featured posts and front page highlight post to focus on your most interesting travel stories and travel photographs. </p>\n<p>The Kale theme is fully responsive so your blog will look great on all devices regardless of screen size and resolution. Itâ€™s a great theme for your travel blog. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/kale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Kale today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find the best WordPress themes for travel blogs. </p>\n<p>You may also want to see our handpicked list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/\">best WordPress real estate themes</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-for-travel-blogs/\">27 Best WordPress Themes for Travel Blogs (2018)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-for-travel-blogs/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5: