arget=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">21. Education WP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-wp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp.png\" alt=\"education wp\" width=\"772\" height=\"361\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223768\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp.png 772w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp-300x140.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp-768x359.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Complete with its own LMS, Education WP is quick to set up thanks to over 14 pre-built demo sites you can install. Or, if you feel like building your site from scratch, you can use WPBakery or SiteOriginâ€™s drag and drop builders.</p>\n<p>Designed to be a multilingual site, this theme is WooCommerce ready and performance optimized.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-wp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Education WP Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/eikra-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">22. Eikra Education</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/eikra-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education.png\" alt=\"Eikra Education\" width=\"774\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223769\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education.png 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education-300x119.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education-768x304.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This contemporary theme is great for a variety of education centers. It comes with the LearnPress LMS plugin, so youâ€™ll have all the features you need to create powerful online courses.</p>\n<p>You can get started quickly with Eikra Education thanks to its 1-click demo import. Or, you can build your site from scratch using WPBakery, the included drag and drop builder.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/eikra-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Eikra Education Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/edugate-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">23. Edugate Education</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/edugate-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate.png\" alt=\"edugate\" width=\"774\" height=\"335\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223770\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate.png 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate-300x130.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate-768x332.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Edugate Education recommends using its theme for schools, libraries, and training centers. Itâ€™s also perfect for home educators and private tutors.</p>\n<p>Itâ€™s a modern theme with a creative flair, perfect for enticing new students.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/edugate-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Edugate Education Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">24. Education Pack</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack.png\" alt=\"education pack\" width=\"775\" height=\"341\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223771\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack-768x338.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As you might expect from the name, Education Pack comes with a â€œpackâ€� of education site demos that you can easily install to get your website up-and-running. These demos include sites for driving schools, dance academies, design schools, and more!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Education Pack Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best WordPress Education themes.</p>\n<p>If you found this post useful, you might also enjoy our article on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress LMS Plugins Compared (2018)\">best Learning Management System plugins</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/\">24 Best WordPress Education Themes (Compared) &#8211; 2018</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"ti