(8, 1, '2018-09-10 12:46:04', '2018-09-10 19:46:04', '<h5>A site about sound art</h5>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFilet mignon ham hock bresaola, chuck drumstick doner sausage strip steak shoulder ground round bacon pancetta tail. Buffalo t-bone drumstick pig, spare ribs pork burgdoggen chuck fatback alcatra sausage shoulder andouille biltong picanha. Shankle t-bone buffalo frankfurter turkey, corned beef venison doner cupim picanha kevin pork chop chicken pork loin. Chuck pork chop flank cupim buffalo jowl drumstick kevin burgdoggen landjaeger tongue ball tip. Doner chuck ground round filet mignon burgdoggen frankfurter shoulder pork loin.\r\n\r\n[metaslider id=\"119\"]', 'What is Sound Art?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2018-09-24 09:39:25', '2018-09-24 16:39:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=8', 1, 'page', '', 0),
