(55, 1, '2018-09-17 09:46:34', '2018-09-17 16:46:34', '<h5>Pierre Schaeffer - Grandfather of DJ\'ing</h5>\n<span style=\"color: #cc99ff;\"><strong>Spicy jalapeno</strong></span> bacon ipsum dolor amet cupim kielbasa sausage, meatball t-bone chuck swine tenderloin. Pancetta short ribs beef frankfurter shankle. Ground round turkey chicken shoulder, hamburger boudin shank landjaeger pig pork chop beef ribs picanha. Corned beef prosciutto ribeye, beef ribs t-bone sirloin alcatra turkey bresaola. Rump pork belly capicola andouille leberkas t-bone turkey brisket drumstick picanha chicken corned beef beef ribs. Beef drumstick sirloin corned beef.\n\nSpare ribs doner picanha pork belly shankle bacon pig pork loin tenderloin flank boudin t-bone. Frankfurter sausage prosciutto shankle doner pork hamburger venison landjaeger chicken tenderloin. Sirloin pork chop jowl, swine pork belly brisket cupim cow pork loin venison. Tenderloin corned beef sirloin, picanha pig pork belly turducken prosciutto. Pastrami sirloin turducken, flank cow jerky cupim rump filet mignon beef ribs pork loin.\n\nPork chop doner beef buffalo kevin flank turducken ham hock. Venison capicola beef ribs fatback buffalo cupim brisket tail. Beef capicola jerky, pork belly short loin buffalo shank picanha spare ribs pancetta andouille tenderloin cow leberkas. Ham hock shoulder beef ribs turducken chicken.\n\nSirloin shoulder ribeye drumstick strip steak. Ham hock tri-tip leberkas tail andouille. Pork loin bacon ham, landjaeger frankfurter ball tip andouille buffalo tongue chuck. Meatball chuck spare ribs cupim, filet mignon pork belly pig fatback turkey. Filet mignon brisket ham drumstick, venison shankle rump landjaeger biltong pork loin buffalo ham hock pancetta ball tip pork chop. Boudin beef ribs jerky pork chop alcatra capicola. Shank landjaeger ham hock fatback, sausage burgdoggen doner turkey kielbasa andouille venison.\n\nGround round chicken alcatra, brisket hamburger ham short loin corned beef short ribs meatball shankle turkey shank kevin doner. Landjaeger jerky pork loin ball tip tri-tip ham hock filet mignon hamburger tenderloin cupim tongue. Capicola porchetta ham hock, short loin cow spare ribs fatback sirloin alcatra sausage doner landjaeger. Burgdoggen cupim sausage boudin, prosciutto swine salami beef pork chop ham hock landjaeger brisket tongue meatball. Jerky kielbasa alcatra tongue filet mignon flank picanha ham hock rump boudin bacon drumstick tail. Hamburger tail bresaola tenderloin, ham beef picanha bacon ball tip spare ribs. Ground round chicken kielbasa, ball tip venison pork shoulder capicola jerky shank.', 'Pierre Schaeffer', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '46-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-09-17 09:46:34', '2018-09-17 16:46:34', '', 46, 'http://localhost:8888/46-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
